#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5a62ec2def4603b504647fd5206131f3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vmstudio\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vmstudio</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Translation excellence has a new benchmark in every respect.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic Program &amp; Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/greg-g-1\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8970e85d74ce48b76ca2a6b00c414cde?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8970e85d74ce48b76ca2a6b00c414cde?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/greg-g-1\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Greg G</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I just stated using Weglot and found it very easy to use.  I did have one question and it was answered in less than 24 hours.  Very much appreciated!!\n\nGreg G</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Weglot made my life so much easier!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/michelleames\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1e6fbaf318c72908d4abccbeeaabdef?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1e6fbaf318c72908d4abccbeeaabdef?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/michelleames\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Michelle Frechette <small>(michelleames)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 5, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I wish I was a polyglot, but since I only speak English, Weglot has my back! The almost-instant translation for my sites into multiple languages means that I can reach a broader audience with my blog and podcast.\n\nAnd the team at Weglot is top-notch! Great people who designed and back up a great product.\n\nThanks, Weglot!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing plugin, super good support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kobaiko\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e29e73effcdde641d0235fd9f5edbc78?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e29e73effcdde641d0235fd9f5edbc78?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kobaiko\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Kobaiko</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I used it and understood how to do everything in minutes.\nThe plugin works awesome!\n\nI needed support regarding RTL language and Samuel answered me in no time and fixed the problem.\n\nBest translate plugin out there, hands down!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dwebr\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c36c2b04d869a0f5c019e737868e7118?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c36c2b04d869a0f5c019e737868e7118?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dwebr\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dwebr</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The support on this plugin is great.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good if it fits your scenario</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hayleen\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/691f1e8cb098f911bb8029bbc3467fb8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/691f1e8cb098f911bb8029bbc3467fb8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hayleen\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hayleen</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple plugin for the users that want to easily translate their website. It does not cover all use cases, but if you just want to generate a translation for your whole website with no hassle, Weglot is for you. Also, great support that will actually read through your questions are comments.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pusonja\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/620d7f1af26349fb7cfb362363946226?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/620d7f1af26349fb7cfb362363946226?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pusonja\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pusonja</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin. I definitely recommend.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gkrasotin\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31effcf1957409a7ecd28ac049bfe3b4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31effcf1957409a7ecd28ac049bfe3b4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gkrasotin\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gkrasotin</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 27, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very quick and easy to start. The application seems errorless. Really nice and robust thing. </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:144:\"Translate your website into multiple languages without any code. Weglot Translate is fully SEO compatible and follows Googleâ€™s best practices.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/weglot.3.1.3.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2009075\";s:7:\"caption\";s:52:\"Example on front end: language switch button on page\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2009083\";s:7:\"caption\";s:30:\"Weglot Translate settings page\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2009083\";s:7:\"caption\";s:47:\"Weglot Translate dashboard, translation edition\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2009083\";s:7:\"caption\";s:30:\"Weglot Translate visual editor\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:46:{s:4:\"1.10\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/weglot.1.10.zip\";s:4:\"1.11\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/weglot.1.11.zip\";s:4:\"1.12\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/weglot.1.12.zip\";s:6:\"1.12